{"author":{"uri":{"label":"https://itunes.apple.com/us/reviews/id957175929"}, "name":{"label":"carla.dug"}, "label":""}, "updated":{"label":"2026-06-22T19:08:43-07:00"}, "im:rating":{"label":"1"}, "im:version":{"label":"45.7.0"}, "id":{"label":"14215084016"}, "title":{"label":"Pire application du monde"}, "content":{"label":"TikTok est devenue l’une des pires applications selon moi. Il y a énormément de vidéos et même des lives montrant de la maltraitance animale. Le plus choquant, c’est que lorsque ces contenus sont signalés, TikTok répond souvent qu’ils « n’enfreignent pas les règles de la communauté ». Comment est-ce possible alors qu’il s’agit clairement de souffrance et de maltraitance envers des animaux ?\n\nUne plateforme aussi grande devrait prendre ces signalements beaucoup plus au sérieux et agir rapidement pour supprimer ce type de contenu. Très décevant.", "attributes":{"type":"text"}}, "link":{"attributes":{"rel":"related", "href":"https://itunes.apple.com/us/review?id=835599320&type=Purple%20Software"}}, "im:voteSum":{"label":"0"}, "im:contentType":{"attributes":{"term":"Application", "label":"Application"}}, "im:voteCount":{"label":"0"}}, 
{"author":{"uri":{"label":"https://itunes.apple.com/us/reviews/id1407326447"}, "name":{"label":"Fatrat72937"}, "label":""}, "updated":{"label":"2026-06-22T19:07:32-07:00"}, "im:rating":{"label":"5"}, "im:version":{"label":"45.7.0"}, "id":{"label":"14215081050"}, "title":{"label":"Very nice!"}, "content":{"label":"TikTok had rose to the top of the internet media. TikTok is one of the most popular apps to EVERY exist. Of course social media hasn’t been here a long time, but TikTok is basically the reason it took off. Rather thats a good of bad thing is for you to decide. TikTok gives you many great chances to connect with other people, find things of your interest, and, and find new hobbies you’ll love to  \ndo. While it is true, TikTok and have a very negative impact on, thats only if you let it consume your life, if you don’t, it is a great app", "attributes":{"type":"text"}}, "link":{"attributes":{"rel":"related", "href":"https://itunes.apple.com/us/review?id=835599320&type=Purple%20Software"}}, "im:voteSum":{"label":"0"}, "im:contentType":{"attributes":{"term":"Application", "label":"Application"}}, "im:voteCount":{"label":"0"}}, 
