{"author":{"uri":{"label":"https://itunes.apple.com/us/reviews/id1730539926"}, "name":{"label":"anum 🎀"}, "label":""}, "updated":{"label":"2026-06-22T17:30:30-07:00"}, "im:rating":{"label":"2"}, "im:version":{"label":"45.7.0"}, "id":{"label":"14214835326"}, "title":{"label":"Tons of bugs and issues"}, "content":{"label":"I started posting on tiktok a few months ago (@anumynumy). However, TikTok has a glitch that affects tons of users, including myself. My videos aren’t showing up on the public search index even though I have thousands of views. Additionally, I can’t even post my own videos to my story. It doesn’t make sense since I had 0 content/account violations or strikes. It’s so disappointing and frustrating to see content creators like me having their experiences ruined over glitches. Not to mention that the help center is 0 help. Tickets are closed without being solved and there’s no way to speak to an actual human being for help. TikTok, do better.", "attributes":{"type":"text"}}, "link":{"attributes":{"rel":"related", "href":"https://itunes.apple.com/us/review?id=835599320&type=Purple%20Software"}}, "im:voteSum":{"label":"0"}, "im:contentType":{"attributes":{"term":"Application", "label":"Application"}}, "im:voteCount":{"label":"0"}}, 
